parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission false neutral/slipping issue can cause the motorcycle to stall or lose power while in motion, leading to a loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The transmission slips into a false neutral
the transmission downshifts on its own
the transmission grinds or makes a noise when shifting
the motorcycle jumps out of gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall or stop running, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or stops running while driving
the fuel pump fails to operate
the vehicle experiences a loss of power
the vehicle is unable to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of fuel pump replacement parts can leave drivers stranded without a functioning vehicle, causing inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The dealer is unable to obtain fuel pump replacement parts
the vehicle is inoperable due to fuel pump failure
the driver is unable to get the vehicle repaired.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear sprocket bolts can cause the rear wheel to lock up, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries.
symptoms: unusual noises or vibrations from the rear wheel
